1. Moj omiljeni parfem je *brenda* Chanel. (My favorite perfume is Chanel *brand*.)
2. Ovo je nova kolekcija *brenda* Adidas. (This is the new Adidas *brand* collection.)
3. Naša kompanija je poznata po visokom kvalitetu *brenda*. (Our company is known for high-quality *branding*.)
4. Kada se bavite biznisom, jako je važno da imate dobar *brend*. (When you're in business, it's important to have a good *brand*.)
5. *Brenda* automobila nije bitna, već kvalitet. (The *brand* of a car is not important, but the quality.)
6. Naš tim radi na stvaranju jedinstvenog *brenda* za našu novu liniju proizvoda. (Our team is working on creating a unique *brand* for our new product line.)
7. Mladi ljudi danas žele da kupuju *brendove* koje nose njihove omiljene zvezde. (Young people today want to buy *brands* that their favorite stars wear.)
8. Znam da je taj proizvod skup, ali plaćate i *brend*. (I know that product is expensive, but you're also paying for the *brand*.)
9. Sviđa mi se taj novi restoran, ali nisam siguran da je dovoljno dobar da postane *brend*. (I like that new restaurant, but I'm not sure if it's good enough to become a *brand*.)
10. Ovaj brend ima sjajan marketing, ali proizvodi nisu baš najbolji. (This brand has great marketing, but the products aren't really the best.)